cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision systems, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper proposes a workflow for training deep neural networks to replace parts or all of a target pipeline, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions reducing computational requirements, which could be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as these fields often deal with optimizing performance and efficiency.
